nt/uploads/2025/04/spyblue-studio.webp\" alt=\"Pagos Puntuales\" class=\"w-full h-64 object-cover transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0b1020]/50 to-transparent\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"card-dark p-8 transition-all duration-300 group\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-center\"><div class=\"md:order-2\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-[#2979FF]/30 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Horarios Flexibles</h3></div><p class=\"text-white/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Disponemos de 3 turnos en horarios 24 / 7, Tu escoges el que más te convenga te esperamos en nuestros estudios en la ciudad de Cúcuta.</p><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center text-sm text-white/60\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-400 mr-3\"></div>3 turnos disponibles</li><li class=\"flex items-center text-sm text-white/60\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-400 mr-3\"></div>24/7</li><li class=\"flex items-center text-sm text-white/60\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-400 mr-3\"></div>Elige tu horario</li></ul></div><div class=\"md:order-1\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl\"><img src=\"https://backend.spyblue.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/turnos-estudio-webcam.webp\" alt=\"Horarios Flexibles\" class=\"w-full h-64 object-cover transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0b1020]/50 to-transparent\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"card-dark p-8 transition-all duration-300 group\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-center\"><div class=\"md:order-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-[#2979FF]/30 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Tecnología de Punta</h3></div><p class=\"text-white/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Disponemos de equipos de ultima generación, somos referentes a nivel latinoamericano, en tecnología e innovación.</p><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center text-sm text-white/60\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-400 mr-3\"></div>Equipos de última generación</li><li class=\"flex items-center text-sm text-white/60\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-400 mr-3\"></div>Referentes latam</li><li class=\"flex items-center text-sm text-white/60\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-400 mr-3\"></div>Innovación constante</li></ul></div><div class=\"md:order-2\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl\"><img src=\"https://backend.spyblue.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/studio-webcam-en-cucuta.webp\" alt=\"Tecnología de Punta\" class=\"w-full h-64 object-cover transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0b1020]/50 to-transparent\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"card-dark p-8 transition-all duration-300 group\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-center\"><div class=\"